Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:36.33,Default,Nagan,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where should I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.75,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me explain first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:41.68,Default,Nagan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:42.61,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:50.47,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,First, the puppeteer who created Minette, Mize Altowirz, is my maitresse, {Teacher in french}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.27,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,which also means my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:56.77,Default,Leicester,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you were able to make such complex automata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:58.68,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:04.64,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,But the only person in this world who can make automata like Minette is my maitresse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:09.55,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It does indeed look like a human girl on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.06,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to have fallen asleep again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:17.85,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,The more complex the automaton, the more Ale it needs to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:20.79,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,She will need some time before waking up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:24.79,Default,Nagan,0000,0000,0000,,Altowirz used to be an adventure comrade in our clan. {Used to be an adventure comrade}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:28.43,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason we have Minette in our care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.41,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's why you knew my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.36,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:35.17,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Then the reason why she called Leicester Papa-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:38.65,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,-is probably because he was the first man she saw when she woke up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.26,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.46,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, where is my maitresse now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.97,Default,Nagan,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we've been unable to contact her recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.67,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Annie-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:54.84,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine. She's still at her old habits...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:04:00.23,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,So, Carina-chan, if it's fine with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:04.76,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll let her stay in the clan house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.21,Default,Nagan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.39,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:14.42,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if Leicester is the father, she'll be like a daughter to me.
