Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.52,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:14.85,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I want a good morning too!
