Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.99,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,Minette-chan sure is kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:18.01,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you allowance; just call me Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.62,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have the feeling you've become a dubious Papa. {Father, Dad}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.15,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle is a funny person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.19,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.72,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about Uncle Verri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:32.49,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle? Well, it sounds rather pleasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:39.06,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one year's worth of pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.75,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:48.78,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Agnes-chan? You're also very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:50.28,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I love puddings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:55.18,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,Eat to your heart's content! I'm the Duke of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.29,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.66,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,So what brings you here today, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:09.36,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah right. You see, one of yesterday's meteors struck the underground treasury of our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.70,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Were there any damages?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.82,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright, Carina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:17.55,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,That's not your usual meteor but a cluster of Ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.16,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:20.18,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:24.50,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Ale is attracted to objects that harness it strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:29.85,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The treasury has numerous objects harnessing Ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:34.86,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, I let the Knights Templar investigate inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.33,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,We felt an unpleasant aura.{Kehai, aura/indication}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.87,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Unpleasant aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:42.88,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the sound of a creature breathing heavily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:47.81,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,It could be because some of the treasure transformed into a Crystal monster. {Shouseki=crystal}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:55.74,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I'd like to ask Clan Oasis to investigate the treasury.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.27,Default,Leicester,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.38,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, we accept the quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:08.09,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,You're even showing professional attitude. That's my reliable daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.35,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:11.80,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.35,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Take it as a way of thanking you for letting me stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.86,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, I want to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.87,Default,Leicester,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is a monster; it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:27.74,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I want to help Papa and everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:31.07,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Minette-chan, we're happy about your intentions-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:33.47,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,No, you should bring her along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:37.46,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,This child is an automaton made by Mize Altowirz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:40.18,Default,Fabious,0000,0000,0000,,She will definitely be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.17,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:44.24,Default,Leicester,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:50.61,Default,Leicester,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to promise Papa not to do dangerous things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.41,Default,Leicester,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.86,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.64,Default,Leicester,0000,0000,0000,,Nina-san, register the three of them as members.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.34,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.65,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's start the quest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.50,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear that, Ritos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:16.85,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.97,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:21.18,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing panties with water-coloured strips, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:22.81,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,I never said something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.27,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,And how the hell did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.35,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Just so that you know, I'm not wearing any.{Nice! d(*U*)b}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:26.89,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:30.81,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to be talking about things like panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.70,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.94,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ritos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:38.55,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true? You're not wearing any? Hey, Ritos...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.57,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Papa, what's a Crystal monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:58.31,Default,Leicester,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly, Crystal is a mineral that stores Ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:03.41,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,It can be made into many items as well as an energy source for automata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:06.40,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,My Montecchia also has some stored in it. {TL Note: モンテッキア Montekkia, is the staff that Carina wields}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.40,Note,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,[モンテッキア (Montekkia) - The staff that Carina wields.]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:10.71,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,If the Crystal absorbs too much Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:15.37,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,...it may materialize into a monster that appears to have a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:18.19,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.58,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,The monster doesn't seem to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.30,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,No, the aura is definitely here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.77,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kind of uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:31.85,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.70,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-san, what's behind that door?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:39.22,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure, I've never walked past it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.60,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,It's the entrance to the Dragon's World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:42.76,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:44.37,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a well-known fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.49,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Even within the Knights Templar, only few know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:51.42,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Under the Verritti family, there is a door that leads to a world where ancient dragons exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:54.29,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,The aura is being emitted from that side. {Timing error from lines 174 to 177. Fixed. -nt}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.28,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have no choice but to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:57.01,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:16.50,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:34.68,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is the Dragon's world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:35.93,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,There's something there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.04,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Above!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:47.02,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Chel-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.45,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon's... shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.37,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Minette-san, stay behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:12.55,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.96,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Look! In creature's forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.45,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,It is indeed a Crystal monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.51,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,But to think it'd actually be so big... {That's what she said! -nt}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:25.45,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.70,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Salsa and Ritos?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:34.70,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget our Golem-chan! {ROFL}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:35.56,Default,Golem,0000,0000,0000,,Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:44.67,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Since it has a treasure's aura, Tortilla Co. will intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.24,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this place to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.82,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.13,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,How did you two come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:57.89,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,We told His Highness, the Archduke, who was at the door, "Papa, please let us go".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:03.52,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,"Hahaha, Papa listens to whatever cuties say." There.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.64,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:09.27,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:13.66,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry, little miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:17.49,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,No attacks in the world can damage this Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:18.95,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right, Ritos?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.98,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,What... Ritos isn't there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:30.82,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,The Golem and... my sister are in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:34.87,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,It's really like you to hide without others noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:37.28,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, even if you are infatuated with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:41.88,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for my sister's imprudence. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:44.46,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,What are you here for?!{Comic relief;what else o.0?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:48.31,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:04.99,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,We got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.81,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.13,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,It's back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.47,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never beat it if this goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:14.63,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.32,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.90,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,The automata over there, I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.96,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,You're Minette, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:26.43,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:28.07,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,What are your thoughts about that shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:31.68,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:37.27,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be in a panic, and looks very troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:38.29,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:41.28,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should communicate those feelings to the shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.59,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.04,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. Just do as she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:57.89,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Minette-chan, if Leicester says it's fine, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:01.36,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but it's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:04.72,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens, I'll definitely protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:06.96,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Minette.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.00,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.82,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow-san, that... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:21.94,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so violent! Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:24.59,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:29.29,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid! Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:32.98,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,If you come over to us, you'll become happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:39.64,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,You're only frightened by the sudden arrival of a huge amount of Ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:42.50,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, for attacking you out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:45.51,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Papa's hands are very warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:54.81,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you should also experience this warm feeling with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.09,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:00.29,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,That light...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:02.03,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely the Anima pearl. {TL Note: アニマペルラ ,魂白珠animaperura=White soul pearl}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.06,Note,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,[魂白珠 (animaperura) - White soul pearl]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.23,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Anima pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.84,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,It drives huge amounts of Ale,and stabilized it. {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.97,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,It's the treasure of our dragon race!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.61,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,You did well, Minette.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.89,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,This child must also have felt that Papa's hands were warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:33.06,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Minette! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:35.33,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:38.62,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I can't feel the strong aura anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.11,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:45.66,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, but thank you for your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:46.80,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.02,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:53.21,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord3\fs37.5\an4\shad3\c&H66C9E1&\3c&H065A7F&\4c&H033045&\pos(769.811361,463.5)}Mysterious floating girl\N Garnet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.64,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Garnet is what I'm called.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:58.18,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,I lent this to that fellow Fabious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.19,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Fellow... Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:04.80,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're actually a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.08,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,That's impressive, warrior girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:08.53,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:13.38,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Dragon's Avatar, the well respected ancient race. {Avatar}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:17.64,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I see, no wonder you're so knowledgeable. {Wise}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:21.18,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Though that dragon's shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.01,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,It should be called the D.C.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.08,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,D.C.D.?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:28.87,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness Chaos Dragon! {Oh dear.....}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:30.81,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.78,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a little too flashy. {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:35.93,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Well... could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:41.33,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,As the Dragon's Avatar, you're the owner of this Crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.58,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Which also means that dragon's shadow is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:50.99,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the meteor's influence, the elevated Ale materialized part of your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:54.70,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean it's entirely Garnet's fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:57.29,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I offered my help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:01.75,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,If it was part of you, couldn't you have handled it all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:06.33,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,I had to use all my power in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:09.23,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can only maintain this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:13.08,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all thanks to her that we were saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:15.89,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:19.63,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Minette, I'll lend this Carbuncle to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:19.61,Note,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,[Carbuncle=Almandine, and is part of a garnet. Garnet=Group of minerals]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:24.28,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something you wish to ask, you can use it to summon me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.87,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.79,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Garnet-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:29.38,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:33.01,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding what you said about Minette-san's core...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:35.14,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, it's an Anima pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:37.47,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something particularly strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.99,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the treasures created by us dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:47.42,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,It's able to absorb and store far greater amounts of Ale compared to a normal Crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:55.28,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Just like earlier, by absorbing the monster's Ale, it was stabilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:20:00.84,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I don't really understand, but will I be able to help Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.19,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.57,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,This is something that only you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:10.58,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, it seems like I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:14.18,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,She's so close to Leicester again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.18,Default-Alt,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah fine, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:17.27,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:27.69,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:29.17,Default,Golem,0000,0000,0000,,Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:34.68,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys are here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:36.69,Default,Leicester,0000,0000,0000,,Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:37.83,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear...
