Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:42.95,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,I, Nick Lu'juck-sama, have brought back a new axe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.18,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:47.57,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like many things have happened while I was away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:48.52,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:52.01,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,It has got quite lively around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:53.08,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Sure has.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:56.48,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bad smile you have there, Leicester.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:21:00.85,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,It's like when you bury yourself making those troublesome items.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:05.23,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Even with your hands full, you can still look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:06.69,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
