Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:33.06,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did it become such a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:40.61,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,S-So what do you think of our swimsuits, Leicester?
